                  </hi>. I am manager of the Commercial Union Deposit Bank and Building Society, 45, Fish Street Hill—we never had any cus<lb></lb>tomer named Walter Hammond—I do not know any of the prisoners this cheque is on one of our forms, and is numbered 20134.</p>
